high_descs: Turn right and move to the counter area between the black refrigerator and the silver range.
Open the cabinet to the right of the refrigerator, pick up the amber colored mug, then close the cabinet door.
Move to the left and face the black refrigerator.

Open the refrigerator, place the mug to the right of the tomato on the bottom shelf, chill the wine glass, then open the refrigerator, pick up the mug from the bottom shelf, and then close the refrigerator door.
Turn left and move to the sink to the left of the potted plant and in front of the window.
Place the mug to the right of the spatula in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk up to the island, then turn right and walk around the island to the counter to the right of the fridge and look up at the upper cabinets.
Open the left upper cabinet door and take the wooden cup out of the cabinet, then close the door.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the cup inside, then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and remove the wooden cup then close the door.
Turn left and walk towards the counter, then turn left and walk towards the wall, after that turn right and walk up to the sink.
Put the chilled wooden cup in the sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled wooden cup in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter in front of you where the two apples are.
Open the cupboard that's in front of you and grab the orange bowl from in there and close the door.
Take a small step backwards then a large step to your left to stand in front of the fridge.
Chill the bowl in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the counter then take a step to your left.
Put the orange bowl in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold bowl in the sink.
